idl_note: No IDL published on-chain. IDL account (6nk4WSTacP7ABh8PGZagoJBL1d4rvHJW3PSdpwctwf6C) does not exist. No embedded IDL in binary.

data_format.bytes_2_9: amount (u64 LE, lamports or smallest unit)

instruction_0x00_arb_swap.behavior: Executes multi-hop swaps via CPI to DEX programs (Meteora DLMM, Pump.fun AMM, etc). Logs 'hop: N amount: X' for each hop. Checks profit and reverts with error 0x1771 (6001) if unprofitable.

instruction_0x02_create_token_account.description: Create a token account with seed for the bot wallet
instruction_0x02_create_token_account.behavior: Creates a new token account using createAccountWithSeed + initializeAccount3 via CPI to System Program and SPL Token.

error_codes.6001 (0x1771): Most common - likely 'unprofitable arb' or custom constraint check (RequireViolated). 39 out of 44 failures.
error_codes.6036 (0x1794): Seen 3 times - likely a specific constraint violation (e.g. ConstraintTokenMint or similar Anchor constraint).

transaction_patterns.note: Uses durable nonces (AdvanceNonce) instead of recent blockhashes for transaction replay protection.
